               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgGaiaStarFormation\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGaiaStarFormation', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: Star formation regions in the Milky Way (<htcite0>).</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "49878bec-a9fb-40b3-9421-cc86648e7a45",
                     "text": "ESA/Gaia/DPAC, S. Payne-Wardenaar, L. McCallum et al",
